00039     record->nativeID = "1";
00040     record->sequence = "DARREN";
00041     record->normalizedScore = .5;
00042 
00043     record = &peptideIDMap["2"];
00044     record->nativeID = "2";
00045     record->sequence = "KESSNER";
00046     record->normalizedScore = .6;
00047 
00048     PeptideID::Record result = peptideIDMap.record("goober");
00049     unit_assert(result.nativeID.empty());
00050     unit_assert(result.sequence.empty());
00051     unit_assert_equal(result.normalizedScore, 0, 1e-15);
00052 
00053     result = peptideIDMap.record("1");
00054     unit_assert(result.nativeID == "1");
00055     unit_assert(result.sequence == "DARREN");
00056     unit_assert_equal(result.normalizedScore, .5, 1e-15);
00057 
00058     result = peptideIDMap.record("2");
00059     unit_assert(result.nativeID == "2");
00060     unit_assert(result.sequence == "KESSNER");
00061     unit_assert_equal(result.normalizedScore, .6, 1e-15);
00062 }
